title: War of the Roses: There Was a Contact Lens in His Bed but He Doesn't Wear Contacts
description: Penny is married but it isn't her husband she wants to do War of the Roses on, it's the guys she' having an affair with.  She found a contact lens in his bed the other day and neither of them wear contacts.  She plans on leaving her husband but wants to make sure the guy she's leaving him for isn't cheating on her too.
